         <div xml:lang="gda">
            <p n="a#1" xml:space="preserve">Ericus dei gracia Dacie Swecie Norwegie Sclauorum Gotorumque rex et dux Pomerensis ♦
      Premisso nostro favore ♦ Swo so<ex>m</ex> wi eth<ex>e</ex>r <cit><quote>før tilscr<ex>e</ex>uit haue</quote><bibl>Kendes ikke</bibl></cit> vm the pe<ex>n</ex>ni<ex>n</ex>ge so<ex>m</ex> wi vnt haue the<ex>n</ex>ne wor thiæne<ex>re</ex>
      <persName>Eggert Gørdtz</persName> aff eth<ex>er</ex> skat aarlike vp at bære vpa wore weyne .
      swo so<ex>m</ex> th<ex>et</ex> <cit><quote>b<ex>re</ex>ff</quote><bibl>Kendes ikke</bibl></cit> wel yt<ex>er</ex>meer vtwis<ex>er</ex> so<ex>m</ex> wi hano<ex>m</ex> th<ex>e</ex>r vpa
      gyffuit haue / ♦</p>
            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve">Swo bethe wi eth<ex>er</ex> oc nw at . j hano<ex>m</ex> th<ex>e</ex>m rethelike gyffue ok
      vntræte / ♦ Thet wi eth<ex>er</ex> <cit><quote>tilscr<ex>e</ex>ue</quote><bibl>Kendes ikke</bibl></cit> vm eth<ex>er</ex> aarlike scat at sende oss tha ær thet vm th<ex>et</ex> aff skattin
      so<ex>m</ex> jke forwiist ær huilk<ex>et</ex> ether bør oss gothe rethe vpa at gøre / ♦
      Men thet wi forwiist haue hano<ex>m</ex> eller nogh<ex>e</ex>r a<ex>n</ex>ner at j thet jo
      vntræte oc betale efft<ex>er</ex> thy so<ex>m</ex> wor wilie th<ex>e</ex>r vm ær / ♦ Ok
      at j haue ko<ex>m</ex>met hano<ex>m</ex> th<ex>e</ex>r vm langer wegh til oss at rithe
      th<ex>et</ex> ær oss ænkte liøfft ♦</p>
            <p n="a#3" xml:space="preserve">Thy vntræt<ex>er</ex> oc gyffuer hano<ex>m</ex> æn genist wte<ex>n</ex> nogher
      tøffri<ex>n</ex>g the pe<ex>n</ex>ni<ex>n</ex>ge so<ex>m</ex> j hano<ex>m</ex> . j swo made
      so<ex>m</ex> for<ex>e</ex> sacht ær gyue scule vpa wore weyne swo gører oc aarlike
      h<ex>er</ex> efft<ex>er</ex> . swo le<ex>n</ex>ge han thet aff oss hauer oc wi hano<ex>m</ex>
      thet vnne wele ♦ Oc hindrer hano<ex>m</ex> th<ex>e</ex>r enkte wtj oc later thet
      engelu<ex>n</ex>d swo fra<ex>m</ex>pt so<ex>m</ex> j noghit gør<ex>e</ex> wele thet oss liøfft
      ær ♦</p>
            <p n="a#4" xml:space="preserve">In Christo valete . ♦</p>
